        description: "Pay-Per-Click (PPC) advertising delivers immediate, measurable results — putting your brand in front of high-intent buyers the moment they search for your products or services. EDMA's certified PPC specialists manage Google Ads, Microsoft Ads, and shopping campaigns for businesses across India and globally, with a relentless focus on maximizing Return on Ad Spend (ROAS).\n\nOur PPC Services Include: Google Search Ads, Google Display Network, Google Shopping Ads, YouTube Ads, Bing/Microsoft Ads, and app install campaigns. We build campaigns from scratch or audit and overhaul existing accounts to eliminate wasted spend and scale winning ad sets.\n\nData-Driven Campaign Management: We conduct deep keyword research using commercial intent signals, competitor gap analysis, and search volume data to identify the keywords worth bidding on. Our bid strategies use automated smart bidding combined with manual optimizations for maximum efficiency. Negative keyword lists are continuously refined to prevent irrelevant clicks from draining your budget.\n\nConversion-Focused Ad Copy: Our copywriters craft compelling headlines, descriptions, and ad extensions that achieve above-average click-through rates. Every campaign includes dedicated landing pages optimized for quality score and conversion — reducing your cost-per-click while increasing conversion rates.\n\nTransparent Reporting: You receive weekly and monthly reports with clear metrics — impressions, clicks, conversions, cost-per-lead, and ROAS — so you always know exactly how your budget is performing. We serve clients in Indore, Mumbai, Delhi, Bangalore, and internationally in the USA, UK, and UAE.\n\nFAQ: What budget do I need to start PPC? Campaigns can start from ₹15,000/month for local businesses and scale upward. How quickly do PPC ads start working? Within 24–48 hours of campaign launch, your ads begin showing to your target audience.",
